atch our findings to the respective quantum group with big center. In the\nsecond part of the paper we match the results to the vertex algebra bundle we\ncompute from the limit of $A^{(p)}[\\mathfrak{g},\\kappa]$, which in our cases\nhave realizations as GKO coset resp. N=4 superconformal algebras.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2022 15:42:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
